9 retailers selling fabric face masks that are worth buyingNot all fabric face masks are created equal.
Luckily, there are many options to buy homemade masks from retailers, designers, and DIYers popping-up online.
After browsing dozens of masks being sold at different stores and what fabrics they are made of, I narrowed it down to nine homemade masks that are worth buying online.
Etsy: Organic Cotton Face Mask from ShiitakeCreekThis mask offers sizes Child/XS Adult, S/M Adult, L Adult.
(Photo: Etsy)Etsy has endless options to choose from when it comes to face masks, this mask meets all the requirements.